# ACS730 Final Project — Two-Tier Web Application Automation

> Automating AWS infrastructure using **Terraform**, **Ansible**, and **GitHub Actions**

---

## 📌 Project Overview

This project provisions a two-tier web application on AWS using Infrastructure as Code (IaC). The solution deploys 6 EC2 instances across 4 public subnets and 2 private subnets inside a custom VPC, with an Application Load Balancer (ALB), Auto Scaling Group (ASG), and NAT Gateway.

Configuration management is handled by **Ansible** and the entire deployment pipeline is automated using **GitHub Actions**.

